Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:42.59,logo2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(892.075,753.75)\fad(100,0)\c&HB70000&}Gertrud
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:45.62,Sayaka,NTP,0,0,0,,好陰暗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:48.80,Madoka,NTP,0,0,0,,要和那樣的東西戰鬥嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:51.88,Mami,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題  我怎麼會輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:57.34,Mami,NTP,0,0,0,,你們退後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:41.61,Sayaka,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:44.99,Mami,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:49.82,Mami,NTP,0,0,0,,在未來的後輩面前  我可不能丟臉呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.09,Mami,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:12.85,kaoju3,NTP,0,0,0,,Tiro finale：義大利語  意為最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:12.86,Mami,NTP,0,0,0,,終曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(937.358,978.75)\fs40.5}Tiro Finale
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:30.50,Sayaka,NTP,0,0,0,,贏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:31.66,Madoka,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害
